er-Kit/dp/B01JZX6K1U/ref=sr_1_1_sspa?crid=3S620FQ7V1MPN\u0026amp;dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.UBSkITaYPjASXjMtv1qRMascZDsqUgQgVYPZ1QZzIdNlryqd4MxnPmHie2MYmUw7a9rHg9gZ4c6syCXgXf_aJRMvBy9bGxajMSvwpySWEOz1RDVFgc3_ope1F76mD2utL9nmt5gRz9YC4NOGQ6NHPXnGgiGCG2QRhesxr2j_63E1YZACQP6pFN6xTcV_yf7SSKe7ryCMrKr5ImaOMkkHngBuqC8MgldKDoRCTVwK0ytJMzGS7rMWpmQq5UjrEnSv1JXqYj24foth00MWdgOpckEjxXreU3IRwp849gzGxrc.q10jceJf4_9iWpyIOP8QrTEfVUhH1Fb7XQFKGHj7Ekg\u0026amp;dib_tag=se\u0026amp;keywords=therapy+stainless+cleaner\u0026amp;qid=1746483842\u0026amp;rdc=1\u0026amp;sprefix=therapy+stainless+,aps,157\u0026amp;sr=8-1-spons\u0026amp;sp_csd=d2lkZ2V0TmFtZT1zcF9hdGY\u0026amp;smid=AGF57ZPIPVW5E\u0026amp;th=1\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTherapy stainless steel cleaner and polish\u003c/a\u003e was like magic the instant I used it. It has a slightly creamy consistency, and when combined with the rag it came with, my fridge went from 50 shades of smudgy gray to the shiny kitchen cornerstone it was meant to be—all in one with-the-grain swipe.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n\n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ca href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button\" data-pin-do=\"buttonPin\" data-pin-media=\"\" data-pin-custom=\"true\" data-ga-event=\"inPageInteraction\" data-ga-event-action=\"Pinterest Share\" data-ga-event-label=\"Article Body Image\" data-ga-destination-url=\"none\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16.9 20.8\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16.8 6.3C16.5 3.2 13.6.4 10.1.1 4.8-.5.1 2.7 0 7.9c0 2.4.8 4 2.9 4.8 1.5-1.5-.3-2.4-.5-4C2 4.3 7.1.1 11.7 2.9c3.2 1.9 2.6 9.9-1.2 10.7-.8.1-1.8-.1-2.1-.5-1.9-1.8 1.5-4.8.4-7.3-.9-2.1-3.6-.4-3.9 1.5-.2 1 .3 2 .3 2.9 0 2.1-1.3 5-1.7 7.1-.2.9-.3 2.6-.1 3.4h1.5c1-1.6 1.6-4.1 2.1-6.3.3-.2.5.4.7.6 1.8 1.4 5 .6 6.4-.7 2.1-1.7 3-5.2 2.7-8\" fill=\"currentColor\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n      \u003c/a\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhA