p)/56112034-23ec-4853-8f87-2a9f43bfe614--IMG_3472.jpeg, https://images.food52.com/MPWgWL-Ta3QSyQePeIw5OF46OGY=/750x1000/filters:format(webp)/56112034-23ec-4853-8f87-2a9f43bfe614--IMG_3472.jpeg 2x\"/\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/BNxXQzsCc-wlx4AjlKa5r6oxzPc=/375x500/56112034-23ec-4853-8f87-2a9f43bfe614--IMG_3472.jpeg, https://images.food52.com/fyluTE3a2cXww9jAC7M8inu7jRs=/750x1000/56112034-23ec-4853-8f87-2a9f43bfe614--IMG_3472.jpeg 2x\" alt=\"After\" width=\"964\" height=\"1285\" data-expand=\"750\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/BNxXQzsCc-wlx4AjlKa5r6oxzPc=/375x500/56112034-23ec-4853-8f87-2a9f43bfe614--IMG_3472.jpeg, https://images.food52.com/fyluTE3a2cXww9jAC7M8inu7jRs=/750x1000/56112034-23ec-4853-8f87-2a9f43bfe614--IMG_3472.jpeg 2x\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cfigcaption\u003e\n          \u003cspan\u003eAfter\u003c/span\u003e\n\n      \u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n              \u003ch2\u003eWhat to Know Before Purchasing\u003c/h2\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eTwo pro tips: First, I’d skip the pack with the pre-moistened wipes. I just don’t find them as effective as using the bottle and cloth, and I’m always in competition with myself to see how little I can throw away each week. Second, if you, like me, often have little nubbins of who-knows-what left on the handles, etc., it’s much easier to get your appliances looking like new if you tackle those with an all-purpose cleaner first and then polish with the Therapy cleaner.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eI used to feel defeated by my constantly smudgy appliances. But now, when the inevitable little handprints and water drips happen, I know I’m just a spritz and a swipe away from sparkling again. I guess that’s why they named it Therapy!\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003chr/\u003e\n\n              \n\n\n  \n\n              \n              \u003ccenter\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eWhat\u0026#39;s your best stainless steel cleaning hack?\u003c/em\u003e\n\u003c/center\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \n    \n\n\n            \n\n\n\n            \n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n\n    \u003cp\u003e\n      Mom, writer, baker, and wannabe SNL cast member.\n    \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ch3\u003ePopular on Food52\u003c/h3\u003e\n      \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
